name: Space Gate
summary:
Space Gate
Inspect. Decide. Defend.

You are a Security Officer aboard humanity’s last refugee spaceship.
Humans and mutants arrive desperate for shelter, but not all of them are harmless. Some conceal weapons. Others hide hostile intentions. Your job is to uncover the truth before it’s too late.

Every decision matters. One mistake can doom the entire ship.

Scan and inspect

Use futuristic tools to scan bodies, luggage, and identities. Detect contraband, abnormal readings, and wanted individuals....
